snippet.title: PartyMan Longplay (Vircon32) [60fps]
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay for the game PartyMan, created by SrxRaposo for Vircon32 console. This game was made for the 1st Vircon32 jam and later completed. Surely it is more fun to drink beer than eat dots lol.

🌏 Vircon32 website: https://www.vircon32.com
🐦 Twitter account: https://twitter.com/vircon32
